rows.label: tlk41400021_06_msg0001
rows.name:
A lot of refugees from Acedia
have come to this city!

rows.label: tlk41400021_06_msg0002
rows.name:
This is a once-in-a-lifetime chance!
Let's teach the people of Acedia
the wonder of wood products!

rows.label: tlk41400021_06_msg0003
rows.name:
If they see my wood products,
I'm sure their sadness
will be blown away!
